<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1357106-is-this-book-shaped-like-a-traingle-as">is this book shaped like a traingle, as the name implies?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1357106'><a id="like_count_community_question_1357106" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1357106?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F108305.Triangle">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1357106-is-this-book-shaped-like-a-traingle-as">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1357106-is-this-book-shaped-like-a-traingle-as">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/40996427-a-j"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/40996427-a-j">A.J.</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It depends on whether it is open or closed, whether it is being held or sitting on something, and what angle you look from. If the book were propped o<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It depends on whether it is open or closed, whether it is being held or sitting on something, and what angle you look from. If the book were propped open on a table with its binding on top and covers touching the table, it would form a triangle if viewed from the front or back of the book. This would probably require the hard back version.<br /><br />However, if viewed when closed or straight on to the cover, it is rectangular, which is ironically the same shape as the Triangle factory.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

<div class='flagAnswer'>
<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1146044" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1146044&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1357106-is-this-book-shaped-like-a-traingle-as%2Fanswers%2F1146044-it-depends-on-whether">flag</a>
</div>
<ul class='communityQAFooter answerFooter'>
</ul>

</div>
