<div id="review_17645289" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/17645289" />
    <a title="Ginny Messina" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/307041-ginny-messina"><img alt="Ginny Messina" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1187999140p2/307041.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/17645289?book_show_action=true">Mar 12, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ginny Messina" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ginny Messina" href="/user/show/307041-ginny-messina">Ginny Messina</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/307041-ginny-messina?shelf=history">history</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/307041-ginny-messina?shelf=disasters">disasters</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer17645289" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16862058470974230802">A fascinating read. It’s not just the story of the fire, but also describes historical trends--NYC politics and the labor movement—that preceded and followed the fire. There is some great historical detail here and von Drehle is a wonderful writer. The fire and its immediate aftermath are heartbreaking and so is the list of the dead at the end of the book. Highly recommended. <br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


