<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2061995591170928606">David von Drehle is the author of three previous books, including the award-winning <i>Triangle</i>, a history of the Triangle shirtwaist factory fire that The New York Times called &quot;social history at its best.&quot; An editor-at-large at <i>Time</i> magazine, he and his family live in Kansas City, Missouri.<br/><br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://us.macmillan.com/author/davidvondrehle'>http://us.macmillan.com/author/davidv...</a></span>
  <span id="freeText2061995591170928606" style="display:none">David von Drehle is the author of three previous books, including the award-winning <i>Triangle</i>, a history of the Triangle shirtwaist factory fire that The New York Times called "social history at its best." An editor-at-large at <i>Time</i> magazine, he and his family live in Kansas City, Missouri.<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://us.macmillan.com/author/davidvondrehle">http://us.macmillan.com/author/davidv...</a></span>
